# Input

```grit
`function ($args) { $body }` where { $args <: contains `x` }

`console.$_($content)` where { $content <: contains `secret` until `sanitized($_)` }

```


# Formatted

```grit
`function ($args) { $body }` where { $args <: contains `x` }

`console.$_($content)` where {
	$content <: contains `secret` until `sanitized($_)`
}

```
